sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Client
    participant IdP
    participant SA as Service A
    participant SB as Service B

    U->>IdP: Request tokens
    IdP-->>U: ID token + access token(aud=SB)
    U->>SA: Send token intended for SB
    SA-->>U: Accepted if audience check is weak
    SA-->>U: Rejected under strict aud/token-use policy